@Yemsc search  for: "Ore no Kanojo wa Taninbou ga Ki ni Naru You Desu"
I doesn't have english translation, I used some programs to translate the game but its a pain in the ass, and it doesn't work all the time, so, I only used it a few times. With that said, its easy to play the game and jump from one route to another because of the "flow system", which allow you to know where you are, which routes are available, which ones you already did and which ones are left, and you can just jump back and forth anytime without getting lost.
You can also play the game in the pov of the FMC, in all the routes as well, you just need to unlock that route with the mc first.
